comment: The burgers are OK, but the shakes are AMAZING!
Been going here for a long time. The food is generally OK. James the server was very rude, but when we had issues management was able to make it OK.
This is the best restaurant in town.
We had a horrible experience here. Bad service, hair in the food, and expensive!
The double cheeseburger is fantastic, but they need to find something different to wrap the burgers in because they can get soggy.
Parking lot is a bit too small and they can get pretty busy. The food is good though.
I went here with my cousins 3 months ago. My cousin from Florida thought that they might have copied some items from Jane's Burgers in Miami. I think the decor is neat.
When are they going to offer jalapenos a la carte?
